; Coverage test for post.cc lines 211-213, 221
; Test get_commodity and get_commodity_is_primary.
; The commodity expression returns the commodity of the amount.
; The primary expression returns whether the commodity is the primary one.

2024/01/01 Multi-commodity
    Assets:Investment    10 AAPL
    Assets:Cash         $-500.00

test reg --format '%(commodity) %(primary)\n'
AAPL false
$ true
end test
